Step 1 : Download the file
https://spring.io/tools/sts/all 

Step 2 : move the downloaded file to /opt/

Step 3 : create desktop shortcut at usr/share/applcations

inside file write 

[Desktop Entry]
Type=Application
Name=Spring Tool Suite
Comment=Spring Tool Suite
Exec=/opt/sts-4.4.2.RELEASE/STS
Icon=/opt/sts-4.4.2.RELEASE/icon.xpm
Categories=Development
